*Gradu* je izgradila velika zidina kako bi se zaštitila od neprijatelja. (The city was surrounded by a large wall to protect it from enemies.)

U *gradu* je živeo mnogo stanovnika. (Many inhabitants lived in the city.)

Mnogi ljudi iz okolnih sela su se doselili u *grad*. (Many people from the surrounding villages moved to the city.)

Nakon što je studirao u *gradu* on je se vratio kući. (After studying in the city, he returned home.)

U *gradu* je bilo puno starih zgrada. (There were many old buildings in the city.)